# UI Components

The app uses Shadcn UI components with custom styling and extensions.

## Layout Components

### MainLayout
- Sidebar navigation (shadcn)
- Header with user profile
- Responsive design

### Sidebar
- Navigation links to main sections
- Collapsible on mobile
- User info section
- Logout functionality

## Page Components

### Dashboard
- Summary cards
- Expense distribution chart
- Income vs Expense chart
- Recent transactions list
- Account balances list

### TransactionsPage
- Transactions table with sorting/filtering
- Search functionality
- Pagination
- Transaction creation/editing forms
- Transaction deletion confirmation

### AccountsPage
- Accounts list with balances
- Account creation/editing forms
- Account deletion confirmation
- Account balance history chart

### CategoriesPage
- Categories grid with icons and colors
- Category creation/editing forms
- Category deletion confirmation
- Usage statistics per category

### BudgetsPage
- Budget progress cards
- Budget creation/editing forms
- Budget deletion confirmation
- Budget vs actual spending chart

## Form Components

### TransactionForm
- Amount input with currency
- Description input
- Date picker
- Category selector
- Account selector
- Type selector (Income/Expense/Transfer)

### AccountForm
- Name input
- Type selector (Checking/Savings/Credit/etc.)
- Balance input with currency
- Currency selector

### CategoryForm
- Name input
- Type selector (Income/Expense)
- Color picker
- Icon selector

### BudgetForm
- Name input
- Amount input with currency
- Period selector (Daily/Weekly/Monthly/Yearly)
- Start/End date pickers
- Category selector

## UI Components

### DataTable
- Sortable columns
- Filtering
- Pagination
- Selection
- Bulk actions

### Charts
- Line charts for trends
- Bar charts for comparisons
- Pie charts for distributions
- Progress indicators for budgets

### Forms
- Input validation
- Error messages
- Loading states
- Success/error notifications
